          <div class="row" id="timeRow">
            <button class="chip" data-time="confirm">‚úÖ 8:30 works</button>
            <button class="chip" data-time="issue">‚ùå 8:30 won‚Äôt work (call me to change)</button>
          </div>

          <div style="height:14px;"></div>

          <h3>Cuisine</h3>
          <p>
            Pick a cuisine ‚Äî I‚Äôll handle the rest.
            <span style="color:#666;">(I‚Äôll pick the dish. Maybe adventurous, might be something you've not tried
              before, maximum romance.)</span>
          </p>

          <div class="row" id="cuisineRow">
            <button class="chip" data-cuisine="Surprise me üé≤">Surprise me üé≤</button>
